---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
---

<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="A quick introduction to my background and interests"
  pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">👋 自我介绍 / About Me</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-800">
      我目前从事将人工智能用于化学合成自动化的研究，重点关注微反应器系统与反应动力学建模。专业背景为化学工程。
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-800">
      I'm working on applying AI to automate chemical synthesis, with a focus on microreactor systems and kinetic modeling. My academic training is in chemical engineering.
    </p>
  </section>

  

  <section>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">✨ 兴趣爱好 / Interests</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
      <li>阅读历史与人文类书籍；Reading history and humanities</li>
      <li>学习外语（英语 / 日语）；Learning languages (English / Japanese)</li>
      <li>研究医学常识与健康保健；Exploring medical knowledge and personal healthcare</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

</Layout>
